description: COVID-19 (acronym of CoronaVIrus Disease 19) or acute respiratory disease from SARS-CoV-2 , is an infectious respiratory disease caused by the SARS-CoV-2 registered virus belonging to the coronavirus family. In a tragic period like what we are experiencing and where the motto is "stay at home", I think everyone is welcome to have a moment of leisure. The reason for creating this token is precisely to brighten your days and make your home days soothing. Fight the virus with us.
name: Covid19
